<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="78" >政景＠鬼兜．E'ciさんは No.7028「PoS CLR1」で書きました。
>You say, 'I choose Alan.'
>Josin Faithbringer says 'Take and read this book. When you are done, hand 
>it back to me and I will summon him. 
>
>Josin Faithbringer から Practical Arts を受け取り、返します。
>
>Josin Faithbringer says 'Farewell. 
>Alan Harten says 'Faith is the key. 
>
>Alan Harten が現われ、Josin Faithbringer が消えました。
>
>You say, 'Hail Alan Harten'
>Alan Harten says 'Greetings, faithful.  Your faith shall be tested this 
>day.  Shall you take the test of courage, skill, or protection? 
>
>You say, 'I wish to test of courage.'
>Alan Harten says 'You have come seeking the knowledge and treasures I 
>possess.  I will impart such things to you, if you do a service to your 
>god.  It matters not who that god may be, but the service and the faith you 
>must exemplify.  Bring to me an ochre tessera, a sky emerald, and a silver 
>hoop. 
>
>You say, 'I wish to test of skill.'
>Alan Harten says 'The test of skill it will be.  Bring to me a golden disc, 
>a piece of dark wood, and a small shield.  You shall be rewarded upon your 
>return. 
>
>You say, 'I wish to test of protection.'
>Alan Harten says 'So, you must be a great protector to have ventured this 
>far.  Bring to me an adumbrate globe, a glowing diamond, and some shiny 
>pauldrons to get your reward. 
</TEXTAREA><br>
